<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Crane Co raised to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Crane Co raised to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Donaldson Lufkin &amp; Jenrette has raised its rating on Crane Co to buy from neutral, a source at the firm said on Friday.</p>
<p>-- Details were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- The company's shares were up 1-3/8 to 29 in early afternoon. Trade was heavy at 527,000 shares.</p>
<p>((--Ian Simpson, Wall Street desk, (212) 859-1879))</p>
